OL,3,CBrit Awards to choose more nominees
OL,4,Cafter row over gender-neutral
OL,5,Ccategories
OL,7,FThe 2024 Brit Awards will select more
OL,8,Fnominees for British and
OL,9,Finternational artist of the year
OL,10,Ffollowing a diversity row over the
OL,11,Ftwo gender-neutral categories.
OL,13,FThe ceremony took the decision to
OL,14,Fscrap gendered categories for its
OL,15,F2022 show in a bid to be inclusive of
OL,16,Fnon-binary artists.
OL,18,FThis, however, led to backlash this
OL,19,Fyear when no female artists were
OL,20,Fnominated for artist of the year,
OL,21,Fwhich went to Harry Styles.
